String Methods
- Useful tricks for strings

String name = "Earl Eal John";

int lenght = name.lenght();
Output: 12

char letter = name.charAt(2);
Output:r

int index = name.indexOf("a");
Output: 1

int lastIndex = name.lastIndexOf("a");
Output: 6

name = name.toUpperCase();
Output: EARL EAL JOHN

name = name.toLowerCase();
Output: earl eal john

name = name.replace("a", "o");
Output: Eorl Eol John

//How to use trim
name = "   Earl Eal John   ";

name = name.trim();
Output: Earl Eal John 

name.isEmpty();
Output: False



